1
00:00:14,120 --> 00:00:17,080
There are three taboos in the executioner's trade.

2
00:00:17,520 --> 00:00:19,600
First, a condemned prisoner biting back.

3
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:22,080
Second, executing more than a hundred people.

4
00:00:22,080 --> 00:00:23,600
The greatest taboo of all

5
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:26,400
is executing those who are neither human nor ghost...

6
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:27,960
Don't ask about their past,

7
00:00:28,280 --> 00:00:30,280
just send them to their final destination.

8
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:33,560
Noon is the peak of yang energy.

9
00:00:33,880 --> 00:00:35,740
Executing someone past this time

10
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:37,840
invites vengeful spirits to haunt you,

11
00:00:37,840 --> 00:00:39,760
and you will be beyond saving.

12
00:00:59,760 --> 00:01:00,920
The time has come.

13
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:02,760
Execute her!

14
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:09,880
Three souls submit.

15
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:12,320
Seven spirits suffer.

16
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:22,240
Fifth Master, noon is approaching.

17
00:01:22,240 --> 00:01:25,039
If we don't execute her now, disaster will strike.

18
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:49,479
Fifth Master.

19
00:01:49,479 --> 00:01:50,880
The time is almost up.

20
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:52,039
Not good.

21
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:13,250
This demoness is too powerful.

22
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:14,880
What should we do?

23
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:21,520
It seems your sword cannot kill me.

24
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:32,760
You brat!

25
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,420
Execute her immediately!

26
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:35,840
You have strong masculine energy.

27
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,040
You can suppress her.

28
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:47,120
Do it now!

29
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,290
Don't forget what I taught you.

30
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:51,440
Golden Knife Secret Art:

31
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:53,240
Sink your waist three inches,

32
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:54,720
flick your wrist seven parts,

33
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:56,079
three inches below the neck,

34
00:02:56,079 --> 00:02:57,280
blade passes without a trace,

35
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,079
no blood seen.

36
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:01,800
One slash ends all grudges.

37
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,330
Do not linger in this world.

38
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:12,760
You brat...

39
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:14,690
You really are made for beheading.

40
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,720
Is it time

41
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,130
for me to retire?

42
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:20,560
Bad news, my lord.

43
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:22,570
Something terrible has happened.

44
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:27,480
The Qing Dynasty has fallen.

45
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:29,440
I just bought this official position a few days ago!

46
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:32,040
Oh my God.

47
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:35,640
You've completely ruined me.

48
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:37,200
All right.

49
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:42,000
Then you can also take over the job as a grim reaper in the mortal realm.

50
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:46,930
So the legends are true.

51
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,220
Otherwise,

52
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:51,780
why did I teach you so much about Feng Shui and Taoist magic?

53
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:55,800
These days, slaying ghosts and exorcising demons

54
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:57,970
makes much more money than beheading.

55
00:03:59,079 --> 00:03:59,920
Let me tell you.

56
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,240
Don't celebrate too soon.

57
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:03,400
Before your 40th birthday,

58
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:05,920
you must pass it to your adult son

59
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:07,280
to inherit this duty.

60
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:09,660
Otherwise, the evil spirit in this sword

61
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,840
will castrate old bachelors.

62
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:13,480
Then I don't have many years left.

63
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:16,279
Don't I have to get married and have a child right away?

64
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:18,560
Then hurry up and find me a daughter-in-law

65
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,920
so I can hold my grandson.

66
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:21,720
Baby, I'm coming.

67
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:25,240
If you want to find a wife,

68
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:27,000
go to a place with water.

69
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:29,000
There will be an opportunity.

70
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,160
Where is there water?

71
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,620
Why don't you spare me one?

72
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:53,200
I finally caught the last boat before dark.

73
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:56,180
Sir, I want to go to Taohua Town on the other side.

74
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:59,000
I'm really sorry.

75
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,610
My boat is small.

76
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:03,040
It can only carry one person.

77
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,760
You two decide.

78
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,040
Of course I go first.

79
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,440
I'm in a hurry.

80
00:05:08,080 --> 00:05:09,640
Why should you go first?

81
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:11,920
Don't you know what 'ladies first' means?

82
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:13,040
Besides, I was here first.

83
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,170
So I should go first.

84
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:14,640
Boss.

85
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:26,700
What are you doing?

86
00:05:29,640 --> 00:05:32,000
I was wondering where the smell of blood came from.

87
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,880
Turns out you are...

88
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:35,520
Pervert!

89
00:05:37,159 --> 00:05:38,760
Don't blame me for not warning you.

90
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:40,120
For a woman to cross the river on her period

91
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,520
is a huge taboo.

92
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:44,920
What era is it?

93
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,760
You're still using such feudal rubbish

94
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:48,560
to discriminate against women.

95
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:54,770
Boatman,

96
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,400
set sail.

97
00:05:56,159 --> 00:05:56,690
Alright.

98
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,460
Scoundrel.

99
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,760
A woman crossing the river in red

100
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:13,520
commits a great taboo.

101
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,440
This boatman

102
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:19,660
is no ordinary guy.

103
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:21,080
Little girl,

104
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:22,160
you are lucky

105
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,160
to have met me.

106
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:40,080
I have a bad temper,

107
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,680
and that brat just made me angry.

108
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:51,770
Boatman,

109
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:54,220
how long until we reach the shore?

110
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,250
Boatman!

111
00:06:58,840 --> 00:06:59,520
Boatman!

112
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:01,280
Boatman!

113
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,040
Boatman!

114
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:12,640
Execution blade draws the moon,

115
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:14,000
lend me some of your evil aura today,

116
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:16,800
to slash through the rivers and disrupt the peace.

117
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,890
The water ghost Qin Xiaoyi,

118
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:29,600
nicknamed the River God,

119
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:34,280
is an important wanted criminal in the Ming and Qing Dynasties.

120
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,840
The bounty for his head

121
00:07:35,840 --> 00:07:37,480
is 50 silver dollars.

122
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:40,460
As for those two little water ghosts,

123
00:07:40,840 --> 00:07:44,159
they just committed crimes in the water with him all year round.

124
00:07:44,159 --> 00:07:45,800
Their bodies are swollen,

125
00:07:46,159 --> 00:07:47,920
and their skin is pale.

126
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:49,600
The bounty

127
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:51,840
is 10 silver dollars.

128
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:53,640
So if we calculate it,

129
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:54,400
the total is

130
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:56,300
a bounty of 70 silver dollars.

131
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,330
Captain Jia,

132
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:57,920
pay up.

133
00:07:58,680 --> 00:07:59,120
Go away.

134
00:07:59,120 --> 00:07:59,980
Get out of here!

135
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,640
Who knows if it's true or not?

136
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:03,440
You idiot!

137
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:04,720
How did you become an official here?

138
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:05,280
I don't care.

139
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:06,140
Pay up quickly.

140
00:08:06,280 --> 00:08:07,140
I'll shoot you!

141
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:07,800
Yes, shoot him!

142
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,530
Captain Jia,

143
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:10,640
be careful.

144
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:12,440
If it misfires,

145
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,500
you'll lose your life.

146
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:17,040
How dare you curse me?

147
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:17,920
Captain Jia,

148
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:20,330
the area between your eyebrows is sunken.

149
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:22,360
You'll lose your house.

150
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,340
Don't move.

151
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:30,440
Captain Jia.

152
00:08:31,840 --> 00:08:32,799
I suggest you

153
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:35,600
go home and take a look.

154
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:38,640
Watch your own backyard.

155
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,680
I'm so stupid.

156
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:57,000
I almost believed that kid's nonsense.

157
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,530
My house is perfectly fine.

158
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,700
As long as my wife isn't cheating,

159
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,860
what else do I have to worry about?

160
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:06,960
Come here.

161
00:09:08,920 --> 00:09:09,560
Go back.

162
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:12,280
Torture that kid.

163
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:13,050
Captain,

164
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:15,280
what if what that kid said is true?

165
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:16,440
Idiot.

166
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:18,720
If it is true,

167
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:19,680
this way,

168
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,800
the bounty is mine.

169
00:09:31,160 --> 00:09:31,920
There's a ghost!
